license: MIT
keywords:
  - finite-element method
  - FEniCSx
  - DOLFINx
  - nanoindentation
  - contact mechanics
  - Sneddon
  - axisymmetric elasticity
  - flat punch
  - frustum indenter
repository-code: "https://github.com/REPLACE_WITH_GITHUB_USER/sneddon-flat-frustum-fem"
abstract: >
  Open-source FEniCSx (DOLFINx) finite-element scripts and Sneddon
  analytical solutions for axisymmetric indentation of an elastic
  half-space by a flat cylindrical punch and a flat-tipped cone
  (frustum) indenter. Reproduces the load-depth response, contact
  stress, free-surface displacement, von Mises field, and the
  FEM-vs-analytical validation figures used in the accompanying
  course-project chapter.
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-05-08"
